OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782638299
OL,3,CITV News reports from Venezuela as
OL,4,Crescue teams arrive to search for
OL,5,Cmissing
OL,7,FAdditional reporting by Washington
OL,8,FProducer Joshua Brooks
OL,10,FValencia airport is now one of the
OL,11,Fmain aid gateways into Venezuela.
OL,13,FAs we landed there were almost 100
OL,14,Fspecialist rescuers from all over the
OL,15,Fworld there.
OL,17,FWe talked to teams from Mexico, Spain,
OL,18,FJapan, Panama, the United States and
OL,19,FBrazil.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
