OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782638299
OL,3,CITV News reports from Venezuela as
OL,4,Crescue teams arrive to search for
OL,5,Cmissing
OL,7,FAll were veterans of earthquakes, many
OL,8,Fbringing high-tech equipment,
OL,9,Fincluding radar, chainsaws, pneumatic
OL,10,Fdrills, and even listening devices
OL,11,Fsensitive enough to pick up a single
OL,12,Fhuman heartbeat.
OL,14,FSeveral sniffer dogs had accompanied
OL,15,Fthem, trained to pick up the scent of
OL,16,Fa survivor in the rubble.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
