OL,3,CITV News reports from Venezuela as
OL,4,Crescue teams arrive to search for
OL,5,Cmissing
OL,7,FThe scale of the damage from the
OL,8,Fearthquake which struck on Wednesday
OL,9,Fnight is still being assessed, but
OL,10,Ffrom what we have seen while driving
OL,11,Fto Caracas, past the epicentre, it is
OL,12,Flocalised, with many buildings
OL,13,Funaffected even close to where the
OL,14,Fdisaster struck.
OL,16,FHowever, in some places, the
OL,17,Fdevastation is breathtaking with
OL,18,Fapartment blocks completely flattened.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
