OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1782638299
OL,3,CITV News reports from Venezuela as
OL,4,Crescue teams arrive to search for
OL,5,Cmissing
OL,7,FThe Venezuelan government is moving
OL,8,Ffast to control media access to the
OL,9,Fworst-affected areas - they are
OL,10,Flimiting the number of journalists
OL,11,Fallowed into La Guiara to 180 per day.
OL,13,FWe saw this for ourselves in Maracay,
OL,14,Fwhere a collapsed apartment building
OL,15,Fwas being excavated for survivors,
OL,16,Fwhere locals told us 100 were missing
OL,17,Funder the rubble - six had been
OL,18,Frescued.
OL,20,FDozens of police and security
OL,21,Fofficials would not permit us to film.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
