OL,3,CITV News reports from Venezuela as
OL,4,Crescue teams arrive to search for
OL,5,Cmissing
OL,7,FNearby locals showed us their
OL,8,Fapartment block, which was still
OL,9,Fstanding, but riven with huge fissures
OL,10,Fthroughout its facade.
OL,12,FInside, entire walls had collapsed,
OL,13,Fand I could see daylight through the
OL,14,Fopen crack along the ceiling.
OL,16,FWe didn't linger long amid fear of
OL,17,Faftershocks.
OL,19,FNancy Viera Costa spoke of the terror
OL,20,Fof the moment the quake hit.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
