OL,3,CITV News reports from Venezuela as
OL,4,Crescue teams arrive to search for
OL,5,Cmissing
OL,7,FShe ran screaming with her one-year-
OL,8,Fold son and her aunt, but it was too
OL,9,Fhard to get out.
OL,11,F"We saw how the walls started to
OL,12,Fcollapse and the pipes burst" she says.
OL,14,F"I am scared to even be here", she
OL,15,Ftells me. "I know at any moment it
OL,16,Fcould fall down".
OL,18,FShe says she will not be able to carry
OL,19,Fon living in the apartment and has no
OL,20,Fidea where she will go.
OL,26,@sD@AOUtD@]O]vD@AOUvD@]O]wD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
