OL,3,CITV News reports from Venezuela as
OL,4,Crescue teams arrive to search for
OL,5,Cmissing
OL,7,FAt the moment, she is living with a
OL,8,Fneighbour for a few days.
OL,10,F"The government says they will put us
OL,11,Fin a hotel, but we are still waiting.
OL,12,FWe don't know what we are going to do
OL,13,Fwith our lives".
OL,26,@rD@AOUuD@OO]
